data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Sneads, FL. Step inside to discover tile flooring adorning the spacious living areas, offering both durability and elegance. The galley-style kitchen provides efficient functionality, ideal for culinary enthusiasts. A vast living room awaits, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Outside, enjoy the serene atmosphere from the covered front and back porches, perfect for unwinding or hosting gatherings. The fully fenced backyard offers privacy and security, creating a haven for outdoor activities and pets to roam freely. Additionally, a substantial 34x32 metal building stands tall, offering abundant storage space for tools, equipment, or hobbies. Situated on a generous 0.48-acre lot, this property provides plenty of room to roam and explore. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a place to call home, this Sneads residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and space for all your needs! Call today to schedule a Showing!
